{"tid":592585,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外交部：霍金去世表示惋惜　霍金對中國的科技進步評價很高","createTime":"2018-03-14T10:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T12:40:24.000Z","uid":188,"like":5,"dislike":123,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"cf4c09479bbca2da6164396efb6eb85c3a5fdff2","tid":592585,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:26:25.000Z","msg":"中國對霍金去世表示哀悼和惋惜，讚揚霍金是傑出的科學家，也是與疾病頑強鬥爭的科學鬥士，為科學、為人類作出巨大貢獻，霍金和他作出的貢獻將被永遠銘記。 外交部發言人陸慷說，霍金生前曾經三次到中國，與中國領導人會面，中國科學家和科學愛好者也與他進行過愉快的交流。 陸慷又說，霍金關心中國的發展建設，對中國的科技進步評價很高。他也十分喜愛中國文化，在助手的幫助下實現登上長城的願望。"},{"pid":"abff3caad4a61d05c75d75800527b272eaf0af4c","tid":592585,"uid":188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:26:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82a4ed6ba88b4b0a553c7aa2bffa1400ee3629d","tid":592585,"uid":144869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:26:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1a9df97bd98b99a98cebdbb2854399f8e15d37","tid":592585,"uid":188,"like":84,"dislike":1,"score":83,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:27:09.000Z","msg":"企開少少啦屌你老母.gif"},{"pid":"7823efbbdfbeb8ba26c12f338b60c972e61a19bf","tid":592585,"uid":188,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:27:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">他也十分喜愛中國文化，在助手的幫助下實現登上長城的願望。</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7701340534a4b2b32ca024ce33c14298fdf3241a","tid":592585,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4aa57a6cc12098a086e13aeab902c12d6bf9ae","tid":592585,"uid":133387,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:32:21.000Z","msg":"<strong>霍金逝世：屢警告中國「天眼」計劃易惹外星人</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180314/bkncn-20180314142738451-0314_05011_001.html?eventsection=int_news&amp;eventid=4028828d4ddd0f1a014df58c60f944f9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180314%2Fbkncn-20180314142738451-0314_05011_001.html%3Feventsection%3Dint_news%26eventid%3D4028828d4ddd0f1a014df58c60f944f9&d=dkR71RwkcYhLNLQ6qeEO%2FgHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=821d5d75\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180314/bkncn-20180314142738451-0314_05011_001.html?eventsection=int_news&amp;eventid=4028828d4ddd0f1a014df58c60f944f9</a></span><br />\n<br />\n英國著名物理學家霍金在家中逝世，震驚全球。對於中國近年在天文領域急速發展，霍金曾多次警告中國，不要接觸外星人。早於中國在貴州建造全球最大的「天眼」射電望遠鏡之時，霍金便對天眼計劃提出質疑，並警告中國停止該計劃，他認為「如果外星人真的在人類發展的這個階段來到了地球，那可能就和哥倫布發現新大陸一樣，對於真哥人類而言或許並非善事。」<br />\n<br />\n霍金認為如此大規模的「天眼」會更容易導致地球被外星生物發現，而如果外星生物到達地球，那迎接人類的可能會是一場災難。在中國去年啟用「天眼」射電望遠鏡後，探測到的第一個可疑宇宙信號，霍金獲悉後就向中國警告：「不要回答！不要回答！不要回答！」。之後，中國科學家又宣佈發現了太陽的分層結構，可以利用太陽當作一個電波放大器，將人類的訊號擴大發送到宇宙中。<span style=\"color: red;\">霍金隨即對發出中國警告，但同樣未得到中方正視。</span>"},{"pid":"8fea588b4478a9e61adba9dde2b6a3951396209e","tid":592585,"uid":81264,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:32:25.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣都可以借黎打飛機<br />\n服撚撚左你班共狗"},{"pid":"d9eca7bf79bf182225a2cad45646fd11d49f2dfd","tid":592585,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:32:35.000Z","msg":"屌你咁都要抽下水"},{"pid":"045a648e0da3a81a427d813913909032d01c0b83","tid":592585,"uid":68080,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:33:51.000Z","msg":"而家真係死無對證<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你 俾人RIP啦 死咗都仲要俾你消費"},{"pid":"2547ec6d3e7ebf2405083277ea8796d9edf03f71","tid":592585,"uid":34103,"like":2,"dis